Coronavirus has changed the world a lot and we are starting to see people across the globe resuming their activities while taking precautionary measures to avoid catching the virus. We are seeing football resume and restaurants have also opened, but Covid-19 has really changed the way we live. These 10 pictures will show just how much the pandemic has affected us and changed how we live: 1. Church members in Soweto practising social distancing  2. Sunbathers at a beach in France  3. A soccer ball being disinfected in Mexico  4. Pupils with their teacher in Thailand  5. Diners at a restaurant in Paris  6. Diners is quarantine greenhouses in the Netherlands  7. Drive in Movie theater in Turkey  8. Outdoor yoga class in Toronto  9. A drive-thru graduation in Las Vegas  10. A salon In Bogota, Colombia  